              ],
              "free_text": [
                " After two weeks from the first chemical",
                "        separation, when the activities of 143Ce had",
                "        completely decayed to 143Pr, praseodymium was",
                "        again separated from cerium by ion exchange",
                "        technique. In this way, 141Ce from",
                "        140Ce(d,p)141Ce and 143Ce from 142Ce(d,p)143Ce",
                "        are distinguished from each other."
              ]
            }
